    "title": "Junior Business Development Manager at HUDCO",
    "description": "HUDCO, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Business Development Manager for our Kanpur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout HUDCO:\nHUDCO is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Referral bonus program\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with HUDCO!",
